{"tid":2491309,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超：破壞份子及港獨份子繼續透過媒體宣揚訊息","createTime":"2021-04-16T08:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T09:36:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f25559c69e600f165fc46228bf94d82a8b8bb66f","tid":2491309,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保安局局長李家超稱，破壞份子及港獨份子繼續透過媒體宣揚訊息。警務處處長鄧炳強則稱，若有證據證明有人用假新聞煽動仇恨，會拘捕及檢控。<br />\n<br />\n李家超：「有一些媒體刻意將罪犯塑造成英雄故事，這些意識非常敗壞。當我們見到歪理，無論通過甚麼手段，我們都要理直氣壯告訴他不對，兼且要大聲發聲，我們的聲音要蓋過對方。」<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強：「很多外部勢力利用香港代理人，用假新聞、假消息的方法來煽動仇恨、分化社會、整造矛盾、恐嚇講真說話的人。我昨天說完，今日看報紙都一一應驗。對於嘗試用假新聞危害香港安全的人，我們一定會全面調查，一有證據會會拘捕及檢控。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=431289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431289&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLdkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=565c4ff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431289&h=d0efc334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=431289</a>"},{"pid":"02efff27a4755589cd0528cdf3c844420598f577","tid":2491309,"uid":370061,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"blue\">香港獨立</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"43b499759a8b3ea8ff910bb2531da8e05d2323d4","tid":2491309,"uid":33352,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"有冇新意，講黎講去都悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf95bdbd72088161af06b381fdf75f77adba5a4","tid":2491309,"uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"依家開始強調「假新聞」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d8526364b944fa2410df13586df5398c7bf903","tid":2491309,"uid":12377